	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64641850"><p>I always try updates on a reasonably similar crash test dummy (or at least a non-critical machine) first. It's just common prudence. Even if that works out, deploy in batches, not all at once.</p><p>Does CrowdStrike even offer that sort of control to admins?</p></div>
