		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~Beeftopia">Beeftopia</a>  <span class="uid"><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~Beeftopia">( 1846720 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
